{"tid":2031020,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中共已經亂了","createTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T07:02:13.000Z","uid":62575,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"323828c8903a50b80509cfe0c636e6b4312112d2","tid":2031020,"uid":62575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:35:10.000Z","msg":"其實雖然我哋好辛苦, 但其實已經見到中共亂曬章法。<br />\n<br />\n佢哋辛苦經營所有嘅維穩政策喺經濟崩潰下基本上無以為繼, 跟住外國積落嘅外交本錢一個一個咁樣跌返出去, 內外交戰基本上已經係窮途末路, 倒台只不過係時間問題。<br />\n<br />\n攪香港只不過係極限之戰, 轉移視線。<br />\n<br />\n外國開始覺得台灣有能力繼承政權轉移, 將民主選舉續步喺大陸落實。 亦唔影響最終一個中國政策。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要繼續推爆佢！"},{"pid":"663296912aa7307e427681743de932d14621d30e","tid":2031020,"uid":76591,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:37:10.000Z","msg":"雖然中國人唔抵幫<br />\n不過如果中共一日存在<br />\n香港人都唔會好過<br />\n香港人企硬！"},{"pid":"f6b80507e843917627b2aa72ae65a55101b3cfd6","tid":2031020,"uid":12628,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:37:57.000Z","msg":"無撚有錯，我地情況差咩，敵人同時都就死咁滯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人唔使放棄，最黑暗嘅時候到了，黎明還遠嗎"},{"pid":"9d15ec8390a9b6f1f282f0449ba4da465d344403","tid":2031020,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:41:37.000Z","msg":"出得呢一招，習囝都係苟延殘喘。證明大家過去一年的功夫，沒有浪費。"},{"pid":"0e63154f6228ec9ad80c8aa853e7ed2e467f67d4","tid":2031020,"uid":329551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T06:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要小心中共詭計，暫時唔好公開用正規武器反抗。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G0LeyI-C6_g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG0LeyI-C6_g&d=s%2ByQnOBpfLb1r8GSWDTSOeNdVtVfIexd6qH9K0u6Sk4%3D&h=e9953a1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G0LeyI-C6_g</a><br />\n<br />\n而家美國已經走緊位打算要中共冚家剷。要忍耐一陣，俾啲時間美國先斷共匪米路。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋香港而家最需要做嘅係：集氣，撥火，每次中共出錯都落井下石。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8130a1e9eb0e6ad0844eee22d2fb44b2fd7ff5","tid":2031020,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"如果台灣接管落實民主，經濟又搞唔掂，立即就變成小粉紅民選出黎既獨裁政權，完全係德國路線～引發第四次世界大戰～<br />\n<br />\n美國接管，實行訓政比較可行，不竟美帝有日本經驗　～"}]}